Package com.coyote.drinknomore.menu Description

Menu package of the application. This package contains all the menus of your application. You can modifiy any of them or even add one yourself. To add one menu, create a [YourMenuName]MenuWrapper class extending MenuWrapperBase and run the orm:menu:update harmony command.
